{"tid":2359731,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【一針見血】著名投資者芒格：分散投資係傻仔行為 一生人三項投資就足夠","createTime":"2021-01-09T06:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T14:27:45.000Z","uid":259777,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"46761d1fbd1f31bd0985dc1e61fccb1129925a58","tid":2359731,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180717/8bb923f21ad44e80b4fd49357a735cfa.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180717%2F8bb923f21ad44e80b4fd49357a735cfa.jpeg&h=24567bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n芒格：   每個商學院都將分散化投資奉為圭臬，我認為分散投資愚蠢至極，我只對具備優勢的公司感興趣。所以這意味著，我不會遵循常規的做法。   如果我有三項佔有優勢的投資，這對於任何家族投資來說都足夠了。   想想看，三項佔有優勢的投資，並且賠率很大，還需要什麼呢？   所以不懂投資的人，可以進行充分的分散化投資，但如果你真的了解你所投資的公司，三項投資就足夠了。"},{"pid":"f3f148d9a11105b90fd91ada6c7f1d0b2ac4abfa","tid":2359731,"uid":68728,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"TSLA <br />\nTQQQ<br />\nARKK"},{"pid":"a3cac56120f6ec4e5f3b89b6a511b4e72ad4f4d7","tid":2359731,"uid":149844,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"一直認為<br />\n<br />\n本少集中<br />\n本多分散<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dce55d86ac2081158c3705ba0cd14024d05c095","tid":2359731,"uid":119512,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"人地同老巴可以見公司管理層, 知道公司運作, 未來計畫 我地一般散戶點得?"},{"pid":"e673a8b5e2ca9de6c59dc3a731df92084de9886d","tid":2359731,"uid":28068,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"一項投資就夠<br />\nTSLA<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三項真係廢老思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ec6f665cb01c0620172cbd7c42c80bf62206eb","tid"